data.description: Absolutely immaculate home in need of new owner. Located in the lovely neighborhood of Vandercroft Farms. Two story home features 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 baths and Bonus area with a large closet. A formal dining room w/wood-grained LVP floor, a kitchen with stainless steel appliances and an island make this home perfect for the chef as well as guests. Spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and fireplace. Master Bedroom has vaulted ceilings, WIC, garden tub, separate shower and dual vanities. A large backyard with a privacy fence makes this home perfect for those warm evening nights and entertaining. Enjoy the community pool area and club house or take an easy and convenient commute into town. Close to Fort Liberty. Make this home yours!
